  "texts": [
    "This can help in understanding complex social dynamics and in designing more effective warning messages and interventions.",
    "ML-Based inverse inference: Inverse ML modeling focuses on deducing the underlying causes, states or parameters from observed effects.",
    "Applied to EWSs, inverse modeling can help understand why certain crisis situations evolve as they do by analyzing the outcomes and working backward to identify the initial conditions or decisions that led to them (avoiding assumptions like rational behavior).",
    "This can be crucial in identifying longterm trends and systemic risks that might not be apparent from direct observation.",
    "Gamification and the data deluge:: Gamification involves using game-design elements in non-game contexts to engage people and encourage participation."
